    <p>LON­DON • For­mula One is in talks with Ama­zon over deals to stream its grands prix, The Fi­nan­cial Times re­ported yes­ter­day.</p>
    <p>F1 chief ex­ec­u­tive of­fi­cer Chase Carey told the news­pa­per that “they’re an in­cred­i­bly im­por­tant po­ten­tial part­ner and an op­por­tu­nity for us to ex­pand and grow our busi­ness”.</p>
    <p>Ama­zon did not im­me­di­ately re­spond to Reuters’ re­quest for com­ment.</p>


